item.title: Need CLASSPATH and PATH codes for jdk 6u16
item.dc:creator: @warlok warlok
item.description:
@warlok wrote:

You shouldn’t need them, go to a tutorial about adding environmental variables, find the path, and replace it.

Example:

The current one says: C:\Sun\SDK\jdk\bin
Change it to the “\bin” path of your JDK folder.
